    "name": "qa-api-restassured (dummyjson.com)",
    "description": "Postman/Newman API test collection for dummyjson.com, covering Users CRUD, Auth, and Products endpoints. Companion to the REST Assured + TestNG framework in this repository -- demonstrates quick, collaborative, exploratory API testing with chained requests and inline test scripts. dummyjson.com is a genuinely free, no-API-key-required public test API, making it suitable for an unauthenticated, publicly-runnable CI pipeline.",
